name: Custom Pet Decks
description:
The perfect gift for any pet lover. A custom skate deck with your pets portrait on it. You will receive a brand new skate deck with a custom stencil painted up to 3 colors of your pet.

Once your purchase is completed I will e-mail you for the photo of your pet for the skate deck. Please allow 10 days for skate deck to be painted and shipped to you.
